# WPF UI

## Files

- `MainWindow.xaml(.cs)` тАФ tabbed UI: Dashboard, Profiles, Advanced; debug suite; settings sync
- `Services/ThemeManager.cs` тАФ System / Light / Dark theme
- `Themes/Colors.xaml` + `Colors.Light.xaml` / `Colors.Dark.xaml` тАФ theme palettes
- `Themes/Controls.xaml` тАФ buttons, cards, tabs, ComboBox contrast
- `Controls/BalanceBoardVisual` тАФ live balance dot + jump banner
- `Controls/ActionBindingRow` тАФ per-slot binding editor (Advanced tab)

## Patterns

- Load settings **before** `InitializeComponent()` in `MainWindow` ctor
- Use `_uiReady` gate in `Loaded` before auto-connect / deferred UI sync
- Use `_suppressSettingEvents = true` when populating controls programmatically
- `UiDetailLevel` controls tab/panel visibility via `ApplyDetailLevelVisibility()`
- Preset buttons: `session.Apply*Preset()` тЖТ `SyncUiFromSettings()` тЖТ `SaveSettingsFromUi()`
- Profile brushes: use `TryFindResource` with hex fallback (Minecraft green) тАФ never assume brush exists at parse time
- Log via `_fileLog.Write` or `session.Log`; UI appends in `HookFileLog`
- Dispatcher: session events may fire off UI thread тАФ use `Dispatcher.BeginInvoke` (not blocking `Invoke`)

## Styling

Reuse `{StaticResource Card}`, `SectionTitle`, `SecondaryButton`, `GhostButton`, `AccentBrush`, `TabControl.Main`.
